==German==
===Etymology===
From the association of the form of a face with the form of a [[pancake]].
===Noun===
'''Pfannkuchengesicht''' ''n''
# (derogative) a very flat and broad face
#: ''Die hat voll das '''Pfannkuchengesicht'''!''
# (derogative) a person with a very flat and broad face
#:''He, '''Pfannkuchengesicht'''!''

